Data are collected through the regular annual survey on municipal waste for the reference year 2008 for the first time.The source of data are municipal enterprises that collected municipal waste. For areas not covered by a municipal waste collection system, the amount of waste generated is estimated. The methodology is fully compiled with EU Regulation 2150/2002.
Data are from Trinidad and Tobago Solid Waste Management Company Limited (SWMCOL). The landfills managed by SWMCOL collect 85% of solid waste.
